1489
01:45:11,340 --> 01:45:13,180
Dead by now.

1490
01:45:14,300 --> 01:45:15,810
Nothing can survive out there.

1491
01:45:17,300 --> 01:45:19,250
Trying to talk Borodin
into more caution,

1492
01:45:19,810 --> 01:45:22,190
saying dinosaurs might wind up
in the Red Square.

1493
01:45:22,710 --> 01:45:24,650
Is there any chance he'll stop?

1494
01:45:24,800 --> 01:45:27,720
<i>Nyet.</i> Borodin used them
like he used me.

1495
01:45:28,340 --> 01:45:31,820
The only monsters
I released in this valley

1496
01:45:31,870 --> 01:45:33,840
are men like you.

1497
01:45:34,670 --> 01:45:36,480
You were told to fetch

1498
01:45:36,600 --> 01:45:39,950
and you happily went
out there looking to kill.

1499
01:45:40,070 --> 01:45:43,510
You madman!

1500
01:45:47,070 --> 01:45:49,820
Do it.

1501
01:45:51,280 --> 01:45:53,810
You are a threat to history.
To the people.

1502
01:45:56,800 --> 01:45:58,620
We need to find a way in there.

1503
01:45:59,810 --> 01:46:00,820
Come on.

1504
01:46:08,110 --> 01:46:09,820
With me! Now!

1505
01:46:32,480 --> 01:46:33,710
Americans.

1506
01:46:34,640 --> 01:46:37,980
General, I found this one
sniffing around the camp.

1507
01:46:38,570 --> 01:46:40,850
There was another one,
but he hid in the trees.

1508
01:46:41,810 --> 01:46:43,580
What is this thing, General?

1509
01:46:43,710 --> 01:46:45,410
You fool.

1510
01:46:46,000 --> 01:46:48,580
Don't you know
what you have done?

1511
01:47:00,470 --> 01:47:02,550
Shut the fuck up.

1512
01:47:05,840 --> 01:47:09,380
-Okay.
-I'm the one that helped
Borodin with dinosaurs.

1513
01:47:09,510 --> 01:47:12,620
This all needs to end
or he will destroy everything.

1514
01:47:12,810 --> 01:47:14,480
The asshole needs to be stopped.

1515
01:47:15,570 --> 01:47:16,810
Do you wanna join us?

1516
01:47:17,610 --> 01:47:19,580
<i>-Da.</i> We will.
<i>-Da.</i>

1517
01:47:20,570 --> 01:47:22,420
- We got incoming.
- Incoming?

1518
01:47:22,540 --> 01:47:24,510
Yeah, big incoming.

1519
01:47:31,140 --> 01:47:32,550
What is this thing, General?

1520
01:47:34,040 --> 01:47:35,550
Get rid of it.

1521
01:47:48,170 --> 01:47:49,480
Don't shoot.

1522
01:49:40,140 --> 01:49:41,450
Go! Get inside!

1523
01:49:45,500 --> 01:49:46,380
Let's go.

1524
01:49:55,370 --> 01:49:57,110
Target on the move.

1525
01:49:57,240 --> 01:49:58,350
...out of my way!

1526
01:50:01,380 --> 01:50:02,220
Okay, let's move.

1527
01:50:03,680 --> 01:50:04,610
Fuck, fuck.

1528
01:50:06,240 --> 01:50:07,620
You sure
about this, Sarge?

1529
01:50:11,140 --> 01:50:12,690
This way! This way!

1530
01:50:15,200 --> 01:50:16,480
Back, back, back, back!

1531
01:50:20,170 --> 01:50:21,190
-Go! Go, go!
-Go, go, go!

1532
01:50:21,310 --> 01:50:22,290
Move, move!

1533
01:50:22,410 --> 01:50:24,680
Follow me. Sergeant!

1534
01:50:24,800 --> 01:50:27,150
- Here, here.
- Inside, inside, inside!

1535
01:50:30,310 --> 01:50:32,220
We go now!

1536
01:50:32,340 --> 01:50:33,710
Wire the collider.

1537
01:50:33,830 --> 01:50:35,710
Do not wait for my command.

1538
01:50:40,870 --> 01:50:41,750
Miller!

1539
01:50:45,840 --> 01:50:47,280
Miller, where are you?

1540
01:50:51,640 --> 01:50:52,750
Demon!

1541
01:50:52,880 --> 01:50:54,780
You demon!

1542
01:50:54,900 --> 01:50:57,920
American demon!
You kill my family!

1543
01:51:14,370 --> 01:51:15,450
Oh, shit.

1544
01:51:21,610 --> 01:51:22,810
Miller!

1545
01:51:32,340 --> 01:51:34,010
- Anyone else wanna be a hero?
- Hands up!

1546
01:51:34,130 --> 01:51:36,080
'Cause this will be
a real quick conversation.

1547
01:51:37,970 --> 01:51:40,020
The collider is still charging,
could go off any minute.

1548
01:51:40,140 --> 01:51:41,020
Get on it.

1549
01:51:42,240 --> 01:51:46,110
Leon, take the Russkies.
Keep planting the C4
and rig whatever else you can.

1550
01:51:46,240 --> 01:51:47,850
-Leave nothing behind.
-Let's go.

1551
01:52:07,170 --> 01:52:08,380
Please, forgive me.

1552
01:52:08,510 --> 01:52:09,820
No forgiveness!

1553
01:52:19,040 --> 01:52:20,150
Miller!

1554
01:52:23,440 --> 01:52:27,250
- You will die,
but we will rebuild!

1555
01:52:29,440 --> 01:52:32,890
God, forgive me.
God, forgive me!

1556
01:52:36,670 --> 01:52:37,950
No!

1557
01:52:44,200 --> 01:52:45,380
Miller!

1558
01:53:05,500 --> 01:53:07,520
- Hey! I thought
all you had to do

1559
01:53:07,640 --> 01:53:09,180
was pull the plug.

1560
01:53:09,640 --> 01:53:11,990
It's too late.
It's set to automatic discharge.

1561
01:53:12,110 --> 01:53:14,250
I have to take console apart
and do a rewiring.

1562
01:53:14,370 --> 01:53:17,180
-How long is that gonna take?
-F-- a few minutes. Then finish.

1563
01:53:18,010 --> 01:53:19,550
-Focus.
-Focus.

1564
01:53:26,370 --> 01:53:28,420
-Sofia.
-Don't worry.

1565
01:53:28,540 --> 01:53:30,650
Husband taught me fail-safes
and I'm never wrong.

1566
01:53:31,540 --> 01:53:32,980
Oh, I-- I hope.

1567
01:53:37,540 --> 01:53:42,450
Vulture One, Vulture One.
Father Vulture. How copy, over.

1568
01:53:43,910 --> 01:53:46,210
Vulture, can you hear me?
This is Six.

1569
01:53:46,340 --> 01:53:51,150
Listen to me, all right?
I want that compound
secured and untouched.

1570
01:53:51,280 --> 01:53:54,810
You understand me? Hello.
Mother fuck-- Hello!

1571
01:53:54,870 --> 01:53:57,850
Goddammit! What the fuck?

1572
01:53:58,370 --> 01:54:00,450
All this fucking work
for nothing.

1573
01:54:01,180 --> 01:54:02,810
You don't understand me!

1574
01:54:03,310 --> 01:54:07,010
You gotta secure the perimeter,
you fucks!

1575
01:54:07,140 --> 01:54:08,320
Fuck!

1576
01:54:12,510 --> 01:54:14,380
Eli coming through!

1577
01:54:14,500 --> 01:54:15,910
Xavier too!

1578
01:54:18,310 --> 01:54:19,250
Where's Miller?

1579
01:54:21,080 --> 01:54:22,090
Miller's dead, man.

1580
01:54:25,000 --> 01:54:26,550
Leon standing by
with the last demo charge.

1581
01:54:26,670 --> 01:54:30,250
-Do you want him to blow it?
-You don't want to do that.

1582
01:54:35,670 --> 01:54:37,080
Oh, you don't know me at all.

1583
01:54:37,810 --> 01:54:41,820
Think about what you could do
with all this power

1584
01:54:41,940 --> 01:54:44,180
and my knowledge. Hmm?

1585
01:54:44,300 --> 01:54:46,620
I've seen enough of your power
and your knowledge.

1586
01:54:47,940 --> 01:54:50,120
- Sofia.
-

1587
01:54:50,810 --> 01:54:53,580
I guess all is fair
in love and war.

1588
01:54:53,700 --> 01:54:55,810
Oh.

1589
01:54:56,640 --> 01:55:01,150
You cannot trust this woman.
She is fucking traitor.

1590
01:55:02,980 --> 01:55:05,310
Oh, fuck.

1591
01:55:10,580 --> 01:55:14,710
Your husband,
he cry like baby.

1592
01:55:18,140 --> 01:55:18,980
Do it.

1593
01:55:23,510 --> 01:55:25,710
They were all better men
than you.

1594
01:55:32,480 --> 01:55:34,410
- Is it done?
- I've done it.

1595
01:55:44,940 --> 01:55:46,150
Fuck's going on?

1596
01:55:50,810 --> 01:55:52,390
Baker, need you here!

1597
01:55:53,140 --> 01:55:54,180
Son of a bitch.

1598
01:55:55,570 --> 01:55:56,550
Oh, fuck.

1599
01:56:09,640 --> 01:56:11,950
You said there were only
six of them that came through.

1600
01:56:12,080 --> 01:56:14,910
<i>Da,</i> depending if Keyes
killed them on his way out.

1601
01:56:26,870 --> 01:56:28,480
Maybe I could have been wrong.

1602
01:56:30,170 --> 01:56:31,250
What the fuck?

1603
01:56:45,540 --> 01:56:47,720
-Holy shit!
-We need to blow
this shit up now.

1604
01:56:47,840 --> 01:56:49,280
Gotta get outta here first!

1605
01:56:49,410 --> 01:56:52,120
Sarge, pop smoke
and get everyone top side.

1606
01:56:52,240 --> 01:56:54,810
Top side? This is the only exit.

1607
01:56:54,940 --> 01:56:56,810
No, there is other side
of collider.

1608
01:56:56,870 --> 01:56:58,250
Pop smoke. Eli.

1609
01:57:02,310 --> 01:57:05,010
-Leon, C4 good to go?
-Oh, yeah, good to go.

1610
01:57:05,140 --> 01:57:06,280
Rig the blow.

1611
01:57:06,400 --> 01:57:07,850
-Frag out.
-Frag out!

1612
01:57:08,570 --> 01:57:10,550
Fall back.

1613
01:57:10,680 --> 01:57:12,440
Fall back!

1614
01:57:14,800 --> 01:57:16,810
Fall back! Go, go, go!

1615
01:57:25,340 --> 01:57:27,050
Run, Sergei!

1616
01:57:30,240 --> 01:57:31,920
Claymore! Set up!

1617
01:57:32,040 --> 01:57:33,510
Setting, Sarge!

1618
01:57:38,010 --> 01:57:41,120
Come on. Fire.

1619
01:57:42,010 --> 01:57:45,350
Come on. Come on. Come on.

1620
01:58:04,340 --> 01:58:06,850
Okay. Uh.

1621
01:58:07,510 --> 01:58:09,280
- Fresh mags.
- Ready.

1622
01:58:09,840 --> 01:58:11,550
You're a vulture now.

1623
01:58:11,680 --> 01:58:13,250
Where the fuck are we going?

1624
01:58:13,380 --> 01:58:14,140
That way.

1625
01:58:27,440 --> 01:58:28,650
Pick it up, pick it up!

1626
01:58:30,640 --> 01:58:32,710
Move, move! Let's go!

1627
01:58:38,640 --> 01:58:39,820
Keep going, keep going!

1628
01:58:40,540 --> 01:58:42,090
Next one.

1629
01:58:46,140 --> 01:58:47,680
- Go! Go!
- Go, go, go.

1630
01:58:47,810 --> 01:58:49,520
Move, move. Go, go, go, go.

1631
01:58:49,640 --> 01:58:51,590
Holy shit!

1632
01:58:52,840 --> 01:58:55,280
Help me!

1633
01:59:05,670 --> 01:59:07,420
- Eli!
- Help me, God!

1634
01:59:11,440 --> 01:59:12,390
Don't leave me.

1635
01:59:13,280 --> 01:59:14,280
Come on buddy.

1636
01:59:16,200 --> 01:59:17,520
Don't let me dying, Sarge.

1637
01:59:17,640 --> 01:59:18,820
- Let's go!
- Eli!

1638
01:59:18,910 --> 01:59:20,420
He's gone! He's gone! Let--

1639
01:59:20,540 --> 01:59:23,710
Let-- Let's go! Sergeant!

1640
01:59:28,610 --> 01:59:29,650
Now, Leon!

1641
01:59:30,410 --> 01:59:32,090
Get up there. Focus!

1642
01:59:32,880 --> 01:59:35,150
-You look after her.
You have to--
-No--

1643
01:59:35,270 --> 01:59:37,450
Go now.

1644
01:59:39,570 --> 01:59:41,350
You're not killing
any more of my men.

1645
01:59:43,510 --> 01:59:45,250
Come on! Come on!

1646
02:00:07,270 --> 02:00:09,820
Spread out! Spread out!
Let's go, 180.

1647
02:00:09,940 --> 02:00:12,150
Let's go! Let's go!

1648
02:00:12,280 --> 02:00:14,250
I need a SITREP, Sergeant!

1649
02:00:14,370 --> 02:00:15,510
Let's go!

1650
02:00:15,640 --> 02:00:16,810
What the hell was that?

1651
02:00:21,080 --> 02:00:22,520
Dinosaurs, sir.

1652
02:00:29,510 --> 02:00:32,180
Where's Baker?
I wanna see that son of a bitch.

1653
02:00:32,310 --> 02:00:33,510
He's not coming!

1654
02:00:35,200 --> 02:00:38,080
Open fire!

1655
02:00:52,040 --> 02:00:54,210
Eat that!

1656
02:01:04,200 --> 02:01:06,810
<i>Incoming.</i>
<i>Stop this fucking shit!</i>

1657
02:01:08,070 --> 02:01:09,150
Hang on!

1658
02:01:41,140 --> 02:01:42,020
Come on, fuckers.

1659
02:01:46,370 --> 02:01:48,180
Keep it coming.

1660
02:02:19,440 --> 02:02:24,810
Colonel, we need
to get the fuck out of here!

1661
02:03:17,340 --> 02:03:18,620
Load up!

1662
02:04:22,880 --> 02:04:25,180
What the hell was
that shit show back there?

1663
02:04:26,370 --> 02:04:29,820
We're supposed to seize
the technology, not destroy it.

1664
02:04:29,910 --> 02:04:32,290
I guess you got
some explaining to do, sir.

1665
02:04:32,410 --> 02:04:34,410
It's all about escalation.

1666
02:04:34,540 --> 02:04:38,180
It's not gonna end
with the destruction
of that fucking machine.

1667
02:04:38,310 --> 02:04:39,950
No, It won't. Look!

1668
02:04:55,300 --> 02:04:56,510
Did you know, Colonel?

1669
02:04:57,470 --> 02:04:58,680
Know about all this?

1670
02:05:00,210 --> 02:05:02,810
-That's classified.
-Just tell us the fucking truth!

1671
02:05:02,880 --> 02:05:04,610
Truth is what I tell you,
all right?

1672
02:05:04,800 --> 02:05:06,480
Well, you wanna know
that the war could end

1673
02:05:06,610 --> 02:05:09,080
with that down there?
That the world could end?

1674
02:05:09,710 --> 02:05:12,310
Colonel! You need to hear this!

1675
02:05:13,670 --> 02:05:15,450
<i>We're getting overrun here.</i>

1676
02:05:15,570 --> 02:05:17,850
<i>It looks like</i>
<i>giant goddamn lizards.</i>

1677
02:05:17,970 --> 02:05:19,050
<i>What the hell's going on?</i>

1678
02:05:21,810 --> 02:05:25,580
Hurry up let's move!
Go, go, go! Come on! Let's go!

1679
02:05:29,310 --> 02:05:30,820
Hey, check this out--

1680
02:05:30,910 --> 02:05:32,410
Hey, get over here!
Check this out!

1681
02:05:32,910 --> 02:05:33,880
Holy cow!

1682
02:05:38,240 --> 02:05:39,280
Come on, check this out!

1683
02:06:00,880 --> 02:06:03,140
Shit.

1684
02:06:51,580 --> 02:06:53,010
<i>The president this morning</i>

1685
02:06:53,140 --> 02:06:56,450
<i>addressed the press</i>
<i>about the presence of dinosaurs.</i>

1686
02:06:56,570 --> 02:06:59,950
<i>That's right. Dinosaurs.</i>
<i>In the South East Asian warzone.</i>

